<style>
  .faq-list-standalone {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .faq-list-standalone__item {
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid rgba(71, 85, 105, 0.4);
    border-radius: 1rem;
    background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.6);
    backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
    transition: border-color 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1), box-shadow 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
  }

  .faq-list-standalone__item:hover {
    border-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.4);
  }

  .faq-list-standalone__item[open] {
    border-color: rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.5);
    box-shadow:
      0 20px 40px -15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4),
      0 0 30px -10px rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.2);
  }

  .faq-list-standalone__summary {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    list-style: none;
    user-select: none;
  }

  .faq-list-standalone__summary::-webkit-details-marker {
    display: none;
  }

  .faq-list-standalone__question {
    margin: 0;
    padding-right: 1rem;
    color: #f1f5f9;
    font-family: "Plus Jakarta Sans", "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.45;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .faq-list-standalone__item[open] .faq-list-standalone__question {
    color: #fde68a;
  }

  .faq-list-standalone__trigger {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 2rem;
    height: 2rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    border: 1px solid rgba(71, 85, 105, 0.5);
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.8);
    color: #94a3b8;
    transition: border-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .faq-list-standalone__item:hover .faq-list-standalone__trigger {
    border-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5);
  }

  .faq-list-standalone__item[open] .faq-list-standalone__trigger {
    color: #fbbf24;
    transform: rotate(180deg);
  }

  .faq-list-standalone__trigger svg {
    width: 1rem;
    height: 1rem;
    fill: none;
    stroke: currentColor;
    stroke-width: 2;
    stroke-linecap: round;
    stroke-linejoin: round;
  }

  .faq-list-standalone__item[open] .faq-list-standalone__summary {
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(71, 85, 105, 0.3);
  }

  .faq-list-standalone__content {
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem 1.5rem;
  }

  .faq-list-standalone__answer {
    margin: 0;
    color: #cbd5e1;
    font-family: "Inter", "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.7;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .faq-list-standalone__summary {
      padding: 1.25rem;
    }

    .faq-list-standalone__content {
      padding: 1rem 1.25rem 1.25rem;
    }

    .faq-list-standalone__question {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }
  }
</style>

<div class="faq-list-standalone">
  <details class="faq-list-standalone__item">
    <summary class="faq-list-standalone__summary">
      <h3 class="faq-list-standalone__question">
        Czy wspolpraca z agentem ubezpieczeniowym wiaze sie z dodatkowymi kosztami?
      </h3>
      <span class="faq-list-standalone__trigger" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
        </svg>
      </span>
    </summary>
    <div class="faq-list-standalone__content">
      <p class="faq-list-standalone__answer">
        Nie, moje uslugi sa bezplatne dla klienta. Wynagrodzenie otrzymuje od
        towarzystwa ubezpieczeniowego, dzieki czemu mozesz skorzystac z
        profesjonalnego doradztwa bez dodatkowych oplat.
      </p>
    </div>
  </details>

  <details class="faq-list-standalone__item">
    <summary class="faq-list-standalone__summary">
      <h3 class="faq-list-standalone__question">
        Jak wyglada proces zakupu ubezpieczenia?
      </h3>
      <span class="faq-list-standalone__trigger" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
        </svg>
      </span>
    </summary>
    <div class="faq-list-standalone__content">
      <p class="faq-list-standalone__answer">
        Najpierw rozmawiamy o Twoich potrzebach i sytuacji. Nastepnie
        przygotowuje oferte, pomagam porownac opcje, a po wyborze prowadze
        Cie przez formalnosci do samego konca.
      </p>
    </div>
  </details>

  <details class="faq-list-standalone__item">
    <summary class="faq-list-standalone__summary">
      <h3 class="faq-list-standalone__question">
        Czy pomagasz takze przy zglaszaniu szkod?
      </h3>
      <span class="faq-list-standalone__trigger" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
        </svg>
      </span>
    </summary>
    <div class="faq-list-standalone__content">
      <p class="faq-list-standalone__answer">
        Tak, wspieram klientow rowniez na etapie zglaszania i likwidacji szkod.
        Pomagam przygotowac dokumentacje i uporzadkowac caly proces.
      </p>
    </div>
  </details>

  <details class="faq-list-standalone__item">
    <summary class="faq-list-standalone__summary">
      <h3 class="faq-list-standalone__question">
        Jak szybko moge otrzymac wstepna oferte?
      </h3>
      <span class="faq-list-standalone__trigger" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
        </svg>
      </span>
    </summary>
    <div class="faq-list-standalone__content">
      <p class="faq-list-standalone__answer">
        W wielu przypadkach wstepna oferta moze byc przygotowana nawet tego
        samego dnia, zwlaszcza dla prostszych zapytan indywidualnych i firmowych.
      </p>
    </div>
  </details>
</div>
